  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Alice和John之间的交互序列图。Alice先打招呼，John回复，最后Alice道别。另外，这两个人最好都能链接到他们的Dashboard和Wiki页面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Dashboard",
        "Wiki"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那链接地址的结构是统一的吗？比如Dashboard都是https://dashboard.contoso.com/加上用户名这种格式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dashboard",
        "https://dashboard.contoso.com/alice",
        "https://dashboard.contoso.com/john"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，完全正确。Wiki也是类似的，wiki.contoso.com下面跟用户名。Alice和John各有两个链接：Dashboard和Wiki。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Dashboard",
        "Wiki",
        "https://wiki.contoso.com/alice",
        "https://wiki.contoso.com/john"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我已经把Alice和John作为参与者加进去了，也配置好了他们的链接。现在来画消息流：第一条是Alice发给John的问候语？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Alice说\"Hello John, how are you?\"，这是一条实线箭头。然后John回复\"Great!\"，这个用虚线箭头表示异步回复。最后Alice用开箭头说\"See you later!\"道别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice-John: Hello John, how are you?",
        "John--Alice: Great!",
        "Alice-)John: See you later!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：第一条实线、第二条虚线、第三条开箭头表示异步消息，对吧？内容分别是问候、回复、道别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice-John: Hello John, how are you?",
        "John--Alice: Great!",
        "Alice-)John: See you later!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这样。整个流程要体现一个完整的简短对话场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice-John: Hello John, how are you?",
        "John--Alice: Great!",
        "Alice-)John: See you later!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。Alice和John的参与者链接都配好了，三条消息也按你说的样式画出来了。你看看还有什么要调整的吗？",
